36
00:01:39,032 --> 00:01:42,436 line:-2
But great usability isn't
the only important goal.


37
00:01:42.469 --> 00:01:45.572 line:-2 align:center
What also matters is
that your app or game is


38
00:01:45.606 --> 00:01:48.008 line:-2 align:center
