39
00:01:48.041 --> 00:01:51.645 line:-2 align:center
from diverse backgrounds
and perspectives.


40
00:01:51.678 --> 00:01:54.948 line:-2 align:center
Our perspectives are shaped
by a number of factors,


41
00:01:54.982 --> 00:01:57.985 line:-2 align:center
